28:33.870 --> 28:35.130
Biar begini,

28:35.480 --> 28:36.550
selagi ada Wen Peng,

28:36.850 --> 28:38.350
semua orang boleh berhubung kait.

28:38.750 --> 28:39.470
Deng Man.

28:40.150 --> 28:41.250
Yu Bofeng.

28:41.790 --> 28:44.000
Zhou Zhicheng, Ding Jing, Wang Qianqian.

28:44.510 --> 28:45.270
Nak cakap,

28:45.290 --> 28:46.040
