29:49.870 --> 29:50.570
Faham.

29:50.990 --> 29:51.470
Qin Yue.

29:51.760 --> 29:52.380
Ya.

29:52.720 --> 29:53.570
Awak

29:53.590 --> 29:54.880
pergi ke Jabatan Pendaftaran Negara

29:55.480 --> 29:57.550
