- Apa hal?

33:25.040 --> 33:25.630
Mak.

33:26.660 --> 33:28.040
Wen Peng ialah anak mak, kan?

33:34.510 --> 33:35.240
Saya...

33:39.870 --> 33:40.670
Betul.

33:45.760 --> 33:46.600
Mak!

33:49.280 --> 33:50.050
Mak.

33:53.970 --> 33:55.060
Dah habis sekolah.

33:55.780 --> 33:57.180
Awak gembira di sekolah hari ini?

33:57.880 --> 33:58.650
Mak,

33:58.680 --> 34:00.090
