36:27.890 --> 36:29.190
Dia berada di Ninghai selama ini?

36:35.750 --> 36:36.350
Sentiasa...

36:38.240 --> 36:39.350
Sentiasa di sini.

36:41.320 --> 36:42.370
Yi.

36:43.220 --> 36:44.780
